<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.8.11">
<l>pulampucīr pūmi yaḷanta perumāṉai</l>
<l>nalaṅkoḷcīr naṉkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉcol</l>
<l>valaṅkoṇṭa vāyirat tuḷḷivai yumōrpat</l>
<l>tilaṅkuvāṉ yāvaru mēṟuvar coṉṉālē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When speaking these ten among the powerful thousand</l>
<l>spoken by Caṭakōpaṉ of good, excellent, good Kurukūr</l>
<l>on the great lord who measured the earth of solitary excellence</l>
<l>everyone will rise to shining heaven.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
